    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab>Nos <persName key="#Princeps" ref="#people/305">Landolfus</persName> divina
                        ordinante providentia <rs key="#Princeps">Langobardorum gentis princeps</rs>
                        concessimus tibi <persName key="#Abbots" ref="#people/332"
                            >Iohanni</persName> venerabili <rs key="#Abbots">abbati</rs>
                        <rs key="#Monasteries">monasterii</rs><orgName key="#Monasteries #Abbots"
                            ref="#juridical_persons/84"> Sancti Benedicti</orgName>, hoc est omnes
                            <rs
                            key="#Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Mention #Function #Redistributive #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches #Property_of_persons_without_heirs"
                            >res et substantias que fuerunt cuiusdam <persName
                                key="#Property_of_persons_without_heirs"><name ref="Vitalis"
                                    >Vitaliani</name></persName></rs> qui <rs key="#Natio">de
                            exteris generationibus</rs> adveniens, sub scuto <rs
                            key="#Tuitio/bannum/mundeburdium">nostre potestatis</rs> subdidit et
                        quiuia ad diem sui <rs key="#Funerary_rituals">obitus</rs>
                        <rs key="#Property_of_persons_without_heirs">filios legitimos</rs> non
                        reliquid qui ei <rs key="#Law">saecundum legem</rs> heredes succedere
                        deberent in rebus et substantiis suis quas conquisitas et paratas habuit,
                        ideo omnis illis hereditas <rs
                            key="#Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Mention #Function #Redistributive #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches"
                            >ad potestatem nostri sacri Palatii advenit</rs>, et quia non habuit
                        potestatem sine iussione Palatii cuicumque de rebus suis tingare aut per
                        quoslibet titulum alienare, propterea omnis illius hereditas, <rs key="#Law"
                            >sicut legibus nostro sacro Palatio pertinere</rs> videtur, sic totum et
                        integrum tibi iam nominato Iohanni venerabili abbati tuisque posteris
                        abbatibus sit concessum pro parte ipsius monasterii Sancti Benedicti, absque
                        illius comitis, castaldeis, iudicis vel cuiuscumque persone contrarietate
                        vel inquietudine, sed perpetuis temporibus tu ipse venerabilis abbas
                        Iohannes et posteres tui habeatis et possideatis iam dictas res et
                        substantias predicti Vitaliani. Scripsi ego <persName key="#Writer #Monks"
                                ><name ref="Ildericus">Ildericus</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Monks">monachus</rs> in anno principatus supradictae potestatis
                        tricesimo, mense Septembrio, indictione quarta.</ab>
                </div>
            </div>
